block slides
  +slide('-1000', '-1500')
    p Learning programming is hard...
    ul.small
      li Common technical problems are frustrating
      li Students often do not feel motivated<sup>*</sup>
      li First impressions are often negative
      li System language such as Java and C++ can aggravate those problems

    p.tiny.right <sup>*</sup>not everybody loves Fibonacci numbers


  +slide()
